{
  "stem": "19218.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 363.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "This is what I have seen the first minute after-- after jumping out of the-- of the boxcars.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Now, of course, they separated immediately the men, women, and children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "My sister, of course, wouldn't part with her two kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "One was still a baby, an infant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Of course, she went on a truck with the women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "My sister-in-law, my brother's wife, was the same thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And of course, my mother, I guess, took one of the children, helping out daughter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they were loaded onto the trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Now, my father and my brother and I were three.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We were set up to be three in a row.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I could assess the situation immediately what was going on in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I mean, they were taking away the kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "They were taking away the women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "They were taking away the-- all the people on one side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And at that time, my father said to my brother, he said, remember, keep him always with you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "He is the youngest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And I-- I probably couldn't imagine or dreaming that they would just take the people and-- and put them in gas chambers right away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "But I realized the situation when it came to the-- they call it selections-- right, left, right, left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "They have sent me with-- with my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And my father told me-- and I realized the situation too-- get over to the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Go where your brother is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And I have jumped over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "At 17, I was as tall, and-- and-- and I had the build, the same build as I am now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "I mean, I was 5' 11' at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And-- and so I could pass as a worker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I guess the face was still young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And somehow I was accepted.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
